## Code Available

The code will be organized and made publicly available upon publication of the paper. If you are interested in using or collaborating on this project, feel free to contact the authors in advance.

## Results

### Quantitative Results

| Methods | Type | USS mIoU | SYN70K mIoU | SmokeSeg mIoU | SmokeSeg B-IoU |
|:---|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
| DeepLabV3P | CNN | 83.9 | 70.3 | 53.85 | — |
| DSSNet | CNN | 86.5 | 73.3 | 53.12 | 49.60 |
| SegFormer | Transformer | 83.6 | 78.0 | 54.98 | 51.67 |
| Conformer | Hybrid | 87.1 | 73.0 | 57.35 | 52.06 |
| SmokeSeger | Hybrid | 88.91 | 75.3 | 58.64 | 53.25 |
| FoSp (AAAI 2024) | Hybrid | 89.73 | 83.00 | 59.03 | 54.12 |
| PSL (PR 2026) | Hybrid | 89.18 | 83.24 | 61.50 | 55.65 |
| **SFIFN (Ours)** | **Hybrid** | **94.7** | **84.6** | **62.19** | **57.75** |

