### Efficiency Comparison

| Methods | Params (M) | GFLOPs | FPS ↑ | Latency (ms) ↓ |
|:---|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
| DSSNet | 29.9 | 79.9 | 35 | 28.6 |
| SegFormer | 84.7 | 45.8 | 41 | 24.4 |
| Conformer | 101.4 | 155.7 | 15 | 66.7 |
| SmokeSeger | 34.0 | 50.9 | 45 | 22.2 |
| FoSp | 47.52 | 66.82 | 38 | 26.3 |
| PSL | 43.1 | 61.3 | 42 | 23.8 |
| **SFIFN (Ours)** | **45.6** | **72.5** | **40** | **25.0** |

> *FPS and latency are measured on an RTX 4090 GPU with 512×512 input resolution and batch size 1.*
